          "text": "A 40-year-old woman complained of unrelenting headache, accompanied by fever, chills, and malaise. After 3 to 4 days, a dry cough developed. Her white cell count was normal. Chest x-ray and CT scan were done. A pathogen I suspected which produces colonies like the ones given below. Which of the following is the most likely diagnosis?",
