          "text": "A patient is seen on the second postoperative day after a difficult abdominal hysterectomy with injury to left uterine artery pedicle with sepsis. A ureteral injury is diagnosed. If the injury had been recognized at the time of surgery, which of the following procedures could have been recommended?",
