          "explanation": "(Refer: Lee’s, Clinical Anaesthesia, 12th edition, pg no:685-687)\nPost-Lumbar Puncture Headache\nEtiology\nCSF leak leading to decreased ICP\nBreach or scratching of dura due to:\n\nLumbar puncture\nMyelogram\nSpinal Anaesthesia\nWet epidural tap\nUncomplicated epidural due to scratching of dura\n\nFactors affecting post lumbar puncture headache"
