          "explanation": "Ref. The Short Textbook of Obstetrics. Pg 120\n \nComplications of PID\n\nInfertility –tubal obstruction from low grade salpingitis\nEctopic pregnancy\nChronic pelvic pain\nRecurrences\nAbscess formation"
