          "explanation": "Ref. API Textbook of Medicine. Pg. 510\nThere are two important Lateral Syndromes. PICA syndrome( Wallenberg ) and AICA syndrome. PICA syndrome is Lateral Medullary Syndrome and AICA Syndrome is Lateral Pontine Syndrome."
