          "id": "medmcqa-a85b26bf-f53f-489e-a7b3-a4e02376cf45",
          "text": "A 50-year-old male presented to the ER with complaints of inability to pass urine. Patient had an accident 1 hour ago. On examination, Scrotal hematoma Blood at the urethral meatus High riding prostate Retrograde urethrogram What should be the next step in the management of the patient: -",
