          "explanation": "McCune Albright syndrome is characterised by Cafe au lait spots Endocrine abnormalities e.g. precocious pubey, hypehyroidism Polyostotic fibrous dysplasia Pathogenesis: Somatic mutation in GNAS gene PTEN gene mutation results in Cowden syndrome. STK11 gene loss of function mutation results in peutz jeghers syndrome. RET protooncogene mutation results in multiple endocrine neoplasia - 2.",
