          "explanation": "Alefacept is anti CD-2 for psoriasis\nEfalizumab is anti CD-11a for psoriasis\nUstekinumab targets the p40 subunit of both IL-12 and IL-23 in psoriasis\nAbatacept is anti CD-80 and CD-86 for severe RA"
