          "correctOptionId": "opt-1",
          "explanation": "This is a case of megaloblastic anemia due to Metformin intake. Lab findings show increased mcv, LDH, indirect bilirubin and normal iron studies, and low reticulocyte, WBC and platelet count. Pbs shows hypersegmented neutrophil. Bone marrow aspiration study shows megaloblasts. Metformin causes megaloblastic anemia as a side effect.",
