          "id": "medmcqa-b31f2ec5-789f-4b6c-98d0-9ba2d38c1dcb",
          "text": "A patient presented with diminished vision and neuropsychiatric manifestations and with hepatic dysfunction.  His eyes on general examination and slit lamp examination appeared as shown in the Figure below.  What investigation you will do next?",
