          "explanation": "Ans- A .Liver. MC organ injury in penetrating injury abdomen: LIVER(42%)>SMALL INTESTINE (34%)>DIAPHRAGM(24%)> COLON (10%).This is referenced from the latest National database of trauma. The commonest organ to be injured in Penetrating or stab injury : Liver The commonest organ to be injured in Perforating injury : Small IntestineThe commonest organ to be injured in Blunt abdominal trauma: SpleenThe commonest organ to be injured in Seat belt injury : MesentryThe commonest organ to be injured in Blast injury :Head above water : TMBelow water : GITThe commonest organ to be injured in Deceleration injury- Duodenojejunal flexure"
