          "id": "medmcqa-a54c4b35-badb-4390-88fb-946424fc5f49",
          "text": "A young married female brought to emergency department with lower abdominal pain and severe dizziness and two episodes of syncope since last 12 hours. Blood pressure on arrival was 89/40 mm Hg and standing BP was not recordable and patient had near syncope on sitting position. Likely diagnosis you would like to rule out -",
